3. edlink.exe — krikzz USB link tool (external pinned submodule)
   Upstream: https://github.com/krikzz/mega-ed-pub
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The daemon shells out to krikzz's edlink.exe for USB communication with the
cart. The public repository pins its upstream repository as the
`references/mega-ed-pub` Git submodule; `edlink.exe` is not copied or relicensed
as an Achievement Box file. `MED_EDLINK` may point to another checkout.
